09-14T08:33:50.000Z","msg":"啲藍絲都識見到人多就縮啦<br />\n知唔知點解佢哋唔喺唱榮光集會嘅時候吹雞搞事?<br />\n知唔知點解佢哋唔喺組團修牆嘅時候吹雞搞事?<br />\n知唔知點解佢哋唔喺大遊行嘅時候吹雞搞事?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為佢哋知自己吹雞唔夠人會俾人打返轉頭啊</span></span><br />\n連藍絲都識敵進我退,去淘大嗰班就唔識,明知冇PLAN好一定唔撚夠人都照衝,重蠢過藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔使問遊行有警察係咪唔去<br />\n屌你咩遊行咪有PLAN定有事前計劃會夠人囉,夠人咪去囉<br />\nbe water唔代表啲water識瞬間移動啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43db0ad0e159126bcd379320f91fee6bb53ce3ab","tid":1568073,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:34:23.000Z","msg":"離遠<br />\n影相"},{"pid":"f72b213967b5a7b591c5f0db6800db8152a64000","tid":1568073,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172ecc5f5330f1e13ae075f6f34cb9d1f35a3fec","tid":1568073,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9574a80c45161d33ff5223d5c6e21b59f62611","tid":1568073,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:34:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914e9cd35be53c09947af5a68485880fcdd85d89","tid":1568073,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c729b94fd5238039653a2b8a955996de81244c","tid":1568073,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624602072f142ea4aad276e98eae5d9fbc496c99","tid":1568073,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14